<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28Mar1917"><font color="red">28 March 1917</font>, <cite>Pound/Joyce</cite> (Ezra Pound to JJ): I want SOMETHING from you, even if it is only 500 words &hellip; I dont want, at any price, to interfere with the progress of &ldquo;Odysseus&rdquo;, but you must have some stray  leaves of paper, with some sort of arabesques on them &hellip; I&apos;d like to start the May number with all of us in it.</div>
